com.coreconsulting.res.openehr.tdd2canonical.transformer

Class LocatableTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.coreconsulting.res.openehr.tdd2canonical.transformer.AbstractTransformer
      • com.coreconsulting.res.openehr.tdd2canonical.transformer.LocatableTransformer

  • public class LocatableTransformer
extends AbstractTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of a LOCATABLE from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model. See AbstractTransformer for more details. The transformation sets the @archetype_node_id and, when present, the @xsi:type based on the definitions in the TDS. The transformation also adds the "archetype_details" child to every element that is an archetype root.

May use the @archetype_node_id and @type for decision logic, and might also use the equivalent path to its definition in the TDS to look up additional information, such as the @valueType that identifies the concrete type of a DATA_VALUE according to the openEHR Reference Model.
